Package: ca-certificates-evrotrust
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ca-certificates (>= 20160104)
Description: EvroTrust root certificates
 This package provides EvroTrust (sub-)root certificates in PEM format.
 Root certificates allow SSL-based applications to check for the
 authenticity of certificates issued by the EvroTrust authority.
 .
 EvroTrust is a Bulgarian official eID issuer with full eIDAS compliance.
